T02TD3257E:16b-1: ma h'a pra tyam gi r'a /
T02TD3257E:16b-4: phyir zlog ma chen mo ni sku mdog nag mo zhal gcig phyag drug ma ste /
T02TD3257E:16b-5: ral gri dang lcags kyu dang mchog sbyin pa ni g-yas pa'i phyag gis so //

T02TD3257E:16b-11: rgyan thams cad dang ldan pa /
